      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented QA procedures and regression test suite.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 is used under an FDA-recognized QMS. Regression test suite covers 47 benchmark cases. Version control and change logs maintained throughout the project lifecycle."
